[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm looking into the `compileJava` task, specifically how source sets work with Java and Scala files. The docs suggest that the Scala plugin can mix both types of sources, using Zinc for compilation. However, it seems Java files under Scala source directories may not be recognized. There’s also the consideration of how task order works between Java and Scala. It looks like I need to verify the configuration and explore options to manage compilation effectively. I hope to streamline this and avoid unnecessary complications!
